#: ../../../release_details/9.5/index-buffer-creation-performances.md:1
msgid "Improve IBO construction performances in vtkOpenGLIndexBufferObject"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/index-buffer-creation-performances.md:3
msgid ""
"For the common cases of triangles-only polydata, the IBO construction time "
"as been reduced by about 25%. It is even more faster if the polydata cell "
"arrays use 32bits connectivity IDs. This can be forced using the "
"`VTK_USE_64BIT_IDS=OFF` when building, or using `vtkCellArray::"
"SetDefaultStorageIs64Bit(false);` or `polydata->GetPolys()-"
">ConvertTo32BitStorage()`."
msgstr ""
